caption: Imported-this-session log
tags: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/console
title: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/console/session-log
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

After every Apply, the titles of imported tiddlers accumulate in
`$:/temp/json-convert/audit-log` (a list field).  The Console renders that
list as clickable links under ''Imported this session''.  The list resets on
wiki reload — `$:/temp/...` isn't persisted.  A ''Clear log'' button forgets
the list without affecting the wiki contents.
